    <string name="about_calendar">About calendar</string>
    <string name="about_calendar_text">The Unusual Holiday Calendar is a calendar created by imperialists from Ententa during World War One. It was created for the purpose of the German Empire, so that people could celebrate so long and often that they had no time to fight for their homeland on the battlefront. It collects holidays, which weren\'t permitted by usual holidays to theirs\' calendars.</string>
